{"tid":956041,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"毒撚哭泣時 (結他哭泣時改詞版)","createTime":"2018-12-26T03:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T14:47:44.000Z","uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85a801d968248ff59ccb4d04a9642183b014319d","tid":956041,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:08:11.000Z","msg":"一張多精多精紙巾<br />\n和一堆一堆瑣碎舊話<br />\n伴空屋中的我坐下 懷念妳<br />\n多麼想性誕妳好嗎<br />\n和他一起開心快活吧<br />\n願他可跟我那樣 活著全為妳<br />\n<br />\nＷoo&hellip;&hellip; 我再笑我似個笑話<br />\n一生都j波多野<br />\nWoo&hellip;&hellip; 我也說過休息放棄吧<br />\n但實在捨不得妳<br />\n只好衷心講一句<br />\n我盼妳性誕快樂<br />\n沒憾沒淚痕伴妳<br />\n<br />\n如他屌你閪 如他說別離<br />\n如果未嫌棄 我即屌臭妳<br />\n無知的毒撚 難解妳別離<br />\n仍不願離去 半哭等奶妳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2a0GYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2a0GYA.jpg&h=d37e7c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我都知作得好尷尬</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9397cba07dec64451871b048fab20bfc8f631a4","tid":956041,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5236d1b7b134a25f768c6cc32e1a2ba871292f0","tid":956041,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa7a51992a2fb0880147598b5d9d0081ea4f2f6","tid":956041,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:13:49.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦   世界好公平   如果人人都心想事成  會天下大亂  世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"335424ffd289b4f35e2269f631d5f557f52375df","tid":956041,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa7a51992a2fb0880147598b5d9d0081ea4f2f6","tid":956041,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:13:49.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇